Detailed Description

Calibration configuration.

The structure is used to hold the information which is required to setup the calibration of the RF

Field Documentation

MMWave_DFEDataOutputMode MMWave_CalibrationCfg_t::dfeDataOutputMode

DFE Data Output Mode: Chirp or Continuous.

NOTE: Please ensure that the DFE Data output mode passed during control configuration and calibration configuration should be the same. Failure to do so will result in unpredictable behavior
